Kaizer Chiefs' new home and away kit has been met with mixed reactions from fans. Chiefs launched the two kits for the 2019-20 season on Monday and if social media reactions are anything to go by, it’s not bound to be a big seller among fans. Chiefs said the kits were supported by the theme #BackToBrilliance. "Bolder than ever‚ the Kaizer Chiefs 2019-20 home jersey is nothing short of confident. The striking new home jersey is an instant classic and features a distinctive and energetic pattern." The eye-catching design on both kits, however, got a major thumbs down from some, while others said it wasn't "too bad". Here is a snapshot of some of the reactions: